subject: What to do...(Sample of UN Fund ownership certificate)
body:
Attention... Jeffrey

We received your emails and confirmation, Sorry for late reply, we have
been attending to other files, we need your full details (Tell no., valid
identity and banking details to receive your fund).. This is not a scam,
and this is the sample of the United Nations fund ownership certificate..
Which is the only legal document required in this transaction....it will
cost you $850 usd...

Fees...$850 usd.
